Our Story

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1507294304091{padding-right: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"]Cherie Bumble is a UK based Womenâ€™s Luxury Activewear label inspired by the fascination of modern day fitness. Our luxury activewear brand is for the modern woman who takes on the world and beyond in her stride and does it well in style. Cherie Bumble offers on-trend pieces showcasing various patterns, colours and technical fabrics to suit the fast pace reality of life.
